The first way
1-> press to creat new  in this list you'll find Edit file template
2-> Click on the add sign to create new template and name the this template
3-> paste the cope of the code 
4-> Apply and Ok

if this way didn't work with you try this

1-> Open android studio
2-> Click on file ,Go to settings -> Editor -> File and code templates
3-> Click on the add sign to create new template and name the this template
4-> paste the cope of the code 
5-> Apply and Ok
by this way the recycler view will work with you
